# HTMX Development Guidelines

## Description
Standards and best practices for HTMX development in the CipherSwarm project.

## File Glob Patterns
- `**/templates/**/*.html`
- `**/static/js/**/*.js`
- `**/web/routes/**/*.py`

## Always Apply
true

## Key Principles
- Use HTMX for dynamic updates without full page reloads
- Keep JavaScript minimal, prefer HTMX attributes
- Use Flowbite components for consistent UI
- Follow progressive enhancement principles
- Maintain accessibility standards

## HTMX Patterns

### Basic Request Pattern
```html
<!-- Simple GET request -->
<button
  hx-get="/api/v1/web/status"
  hx-target="#status-display"
  hx-trigger="click"
  class="text-white bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-2.5">
  Refresh Status
</button>

<!-- Target element -->
<div id="status-display" class="mt-4">
  <!-- Content will be replaced here -->
</div>
```

### Form Submission
```html
<!-- Form with validation -->
<form hx-post="/api/v1/web/agents"
      hx-target="#agent-list"
      hx-swap="beforeend"
      class="space-y-4">
  <div>
    <label class="block mb-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
      Agent Name
    </label>
    <input type="text"
           name="agent_name"
           required
           class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-300 text-gray-900 text-sm rounded-lg focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 block w-full p-2.5">
  </div>
  <button type="submit"
          class="text-white bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-2.5">
    Add Agent
  </button>
</form>
```

### Real-time Updates
```html
<!-- Polling for updates -->
<div hx-get="/api/v1/web/tasks/status"
     hx-trigger="every 2s"
     hx-target="#task-status">
  <!-- Status content -->
</div>

<!-- Server-Sent Events -->
<div hx-sse="connect:/api/v1/web/events">
  <div hx-sse="swap:message">
    <!-- Real-time updates -->
  </div>
</div>
```

### Modal Dialogs
```html
<!-- Trigger button -->
<button hx-get="/api/v1/web/agents/new"
        hx-target="#modal-content"
        hx-trigger="click"
        class="text-white bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-2.5">
  New Agent
</button>

<!-- Modal structure -->
<div id="modal"
     class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 hidden w-full p-4 overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto md:inset-0 h-[calc(100%-1rem)] max-h-full">
  <div class="relative w-full max-w-2xl max-h-full">
    <div class="relative bg-white rounded-lg shadow dark:bg-gray-700">
      <div id="modal-content">
        <!-- Modal content loaded here -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```

### Progress Indicators
```html
<!-- Loading states -->
<button hx-get="/api/v1/web/tasks/start"
        hx-indicator="#spinner"
        class="text-white bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-2.5">
  Start Task
</button>

<div id="spinner"
     class="htmx-indicator">
  <div class="animate-spin rounded-full h-8 w-8 border-b-2 border-gray-900"></div>
</div>
```

### Error Handling
```html
<!-- Error template -->
<div id="error-template"
     class="p-4 mb-4 text-sm text-red-800 rounded-lg bg-red-50 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-red-400"
     role="alert">
  <span class="font-medium">Error!</span>
  <span id="error-message"></span>
</div>

<!-- Error trigger -->
<div hx-get="/api/v1/web/data"
     hx-target="#content"
     hx-error-target="#error-template"
     hx-error-message="Failed to load data">
  <!-- Content -->
</div>
```

